description: Beneath an etched seaglass ceiling, a silken sea-themed tapestry hangs on one of the glazed bamboo walls.  A heavy lead glass display case and a shell-lined bamboo counter sit in opposite corners while a braided seagrass rug rests on a glazed bamboo floor.
